            <scopecontent id="aspace_3e7308ad3ca9628e271beaaabe1edc1e">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The approximately 40 minute film includes: Lei Tai-Fu Arrives (assumed to be Dr. Lyman arriving home), Taking Down Ping, Central Park, Street Scenes, Street Kitchens, Miss China 1937, Chinese New Year, Ling Fu SSU, Peiping Union Medical College, Social Service Unit, Yenching University, Pilgrimage to Maio Feng Shrine, Street Parade, U.S. Troops Parading, Japanese Planes July 1937, Summer Palace, Pei Hai, National Library, Temple of Heaven, Funeral Procession, U.S. Marines, Belka (Mrs. Lyman's horse), Lei Hwang Teh (Mrs. Lyman's dog), and Ting Tsien (the woman who appears a few times is surely Mrs. Lyman).</p>
            </scopecontent>
